features: 【Big Suction, Big Motor, Big Tank】 Combining a 0.88QT easy-to-empty dust tank with a powerful 600W digital motor and a 20kPa strong suction, this versatile carpet vacuum cleaner expertly cleans pet dander, hair, dust, and particles.

【Movement Made Manageable】 Capable of cleaning a radius that’s up to 30 feet, this corded stick vacuum cleaner with its 32ft long power cord can easily get around the large homes. Once done, the power cord can be neatly wrapped around a built-in winding hook so it’s out of the way until the next clean.

【5-in-1 Cleaner Does It Better】 With a stick design that favors minimalism, this lightweight handheld stick vacuum cleaner features a no-roller design so hair doesn’t get tangled, as well as 4 multifunctional brush heads, enabling it to clean the floors, shutters, sofa seams, vehicles, and more.

【Portable Vacuum Without Bulk】By focusing on a slim build, this 3.5lbs lightweight stick vacuum is easy to handle, leading to effortless cleaning. Ideal for minimalists who don’t have space, simply stand the vacuum against the wall once cleaning is done.

【Assorted Brushes Clean Most Surfaces】 Whether it’s short-pile carpets, medium-pile carpets, wooden floors, and ceramic tiles or something else, this bagless stick vacuum includes a selection of brushes, ensuring a deep, satisfying clean.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Small and mighty
reviews.reviewText: This vacuum is more than meets the eye! For its size it has powerful suction.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice device
reviews.reviewText: We got this to replace a hand-held unit that just wasn't powerful enough. We love that this is more powerful. Yes it has a cord, but that's likely why it's as powerful as it is. And the cord is very long. Plus it's easy to get under chairs and tables. No more getting down on our hands and knees! (Which we're getting too old for anyway.) Can't wait to use it in the car.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a really nifty little vacuum, especially for hardwood floor, cars, or tight to reach places. The suction is really powerful, but the vacuum itself is still really light. The long handle extension comes off, allowing for a small handheld unit that is really agile and great for getting into nooks and crannies. For the price, I can confidently say it beats out other name brand vacuums for value!

reviews.reviewText: I've always wanted a Small Vacuum Cleaner with big suction, Compared a lot of brand styles, Find that other brands of Small Vacuum Cleaner will be a little cheaper by comparison, But look at other buyers feedback product quality is not very good, and all said that suction is poor, After I used this Aspiron Small Vacuum Cleaner, Its suction is really strong, The slit head is perfect for cleaning the cracks on my sofa, Happy to get the Small Vacuum Cleaner I wanted!
